Detailed Description

The KeyMsgGenerator is a Subsystem, which processes incoming key-data from ATC by using the AT-command at+ckpd. The ATC string is parsed by the AtKeyParser and translated into APOXI key messages. This SubSystem must be actived, for example when automatic testing should be applied.
